Login into the AWS console 
Click on launch instances, then click next for further steps like tags, storage, configure, etc.
Create a new key pair and click on launch instances
In the left menu choose a load balancer
Create load balancer
Choose availability zone as same as your instances
Set the target group for current running instances
The create load balancer
Go to the security groups, create new security groups
Click on the outbound rule, edit the outbound rule, and set as all traffic allowed, set the source as anywhere IPV4
Check the inbound rules
Edit the inbound and outbound rules
In inbound choose type as HTTP and SOURCE as anywhere IPV4


